This paper discusses the use of natural language processing and deep learning techniques in building an intelligent tutoring system for student learning. Therefore, it is likely to belong to the arXiv CS sub-categories of Computational Linguistics (cs.CL), Machine Learning (cs.LG), Artificial Intelligence (cs.AI), Education (cs.ED), and Human-Computer Interaction (cs.HC).
